library(dplyr)
library(astsa)

clean_birthrates <- filter(raw_birthrates, Date!="Daily total female births in California")
colnames(clean_birthrates) <-  c('date',"daily_female_births")
clean_birthrates$date <- as.Date(clean_birthrates$date)
